Usage: set_socv_rc_variation_factor [-help] <variation_factor> [-early] [-late]
                                    [-view <list_of_views>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<variation_factor>        # Specifies the value of the interconnect delay
                          # variation factor to be used (float, required)
-early                    # Specifies the variation factor for early
                          # interconnect delays (bool, optional)
-late                     # Specifies the variation factor for late
                          # interconnect delays (bool, optional)
-view <list_of_views>     # Apply the SOCV interconnect variation factor to the
                          # specified list of analysis views. (string, optional)